  <!-- Helpful tip -->
  <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-amber-900">
    <p class="text-sm">
      Need paper tags or a quick line spool? Call first—services vary by location. You can also buy licenses online via ODFW and check the Willamette Zone regulations before you go:
      <a href="https://odfw.huntfishoregon.com/" class="underline decoration-amber-400 underline-offset-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buy license</a> ·
